main event: A woman reported seeing a bright object in the sky over Janesville, Wisconsin on February 5, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as a round shape with four flashing lights,The sighting lasted approximately 3-4 minutes,The object hovered and then gradually increased in speed before disappearing,Another witness reported a similar sighting in the area on January 24, 1965,The report was made to local radio shortly after the sighting occurred.
sighted object: a bright round object with flashing lights
witness description: One witness is a 73-year-old female; another witness is a neighbor who saw a similar object.
